room_title: Escape room "The Mall" by Complexity: A Puzzling Adventure in Hartford
room_description: You’ve been shopping at the Complex City Mall all day. It’s almost time for your dinner reservation so you start heading for your car. As you are leaving, you discover you’ve left behind a few of your belongings (including your keys and wallet!) and the stores are closed for the night. Can you find your things and a way to get into the locked parking garage with enough time to make your dinner reservation?
